Implemented, pushed, opened PR, and replied on the discussion.

PR: [jdx/mise#10707](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/10707)  
Discussion reply: [comment](https://github.com/jdx/mise/discussions/10667#discussioncomment-17503439)

Behavior note: existing subproject lockfiles auto-migrate into root lockfiles on lock-aware mutating flows when unified monorepo lockfiles are enabled and explicit `config_roots` exist. Older mise versions will not understand unified root lockfiles for subproject-owned tools, so mixed-version teams should use `[monorepo] lockfile = false`.

Verified with `mise run build`, `cargo test -q lockfile`, `cargo test -q monorepo`, targeted e2e tests, `mise run render:usage`, and `mise run lint-fix`.

